WEBVTT

01:40.509 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.289 --> 01:48.789
[Episode 17]

02:56.010 --> 02:56.800
Well...

03:00.080 --> 03:00.960
Mrs. Zhao.

03:02.930 --> 03:04.120
Could you please not

03:06.360 --> 03:08.620
tell my dad about what happened just now?

03:23.520 --> 03:24.290
Mu,

03:24.660 --> 03:25.700
I probably

03:26.610 --> 03:28.960
shouldn't be the one saying this,

03:30.079 --> 03:32.120
but I've watched Zhao grow up.

03:32.930 --> 03:34.120
Life hasn't been easy on him these years.

03:34.120 --> 03:35.450
He's been through a lot.

03:36.460 --> 03:37.930
He's a reliable young man.

03:39.240 --> 03:40.079
But I think...

03:44.680 --> 03:45.560
Your mom

03:46.490 --> 03:48.020
definitely won't approve.

03:49.120 --> 03:50.010
You really need

03:50.840 --> 03:52.700
to think this through carefully.

03:55.840 --> 03:57.120
Honestly speaking,

03:58.480 --> 04:00.520
I want Zhao to lead a good life.

04:03.040 --> 04:04.770
Actually, since you came here,

04:05.400 --> 04:06.730
I've already noticed

04:07.840 --> 04:09.240
that you've had your mind

04:09.840 --> 04:11.290
on him this whole time.

04:14.080 --> 04:16.010
I came here just for him.

04:17.050 --> 04:19.050
And I stayed for him, too.

04:23.760 --> 04:24.650
Mrs. Zhao,

04:25.410 --> 04:26.850
please help me.

04:41.490 --> 04:43.170
Then let's just pretend

04:48.610 --> 04:49.680
that I didn't see

04:50.380 --> 04:51.590
what happened today.

04:54.409 --> 04:55.490
Go get some rest.

05:14.320 --> 05:15.000
How's it?

05:15.880 --> 05:17.080
Did you find Jiang Mu?

05:17.320 --> 05:18.780
He's in Jin Qiang's place.

05:20.050 --> 05:21.050
When you called me,

05:21.050 --> 05:22.610
I was almost worried sick.

05:23.410 --> 05:24.240
Is she okay?

05:26.650 --> 05:27.800
Listen, this is your fault.

05:27.800 --> 05:30.130
You didn't explain things clearly to her.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.820
This is way too dangerous.

05:32.290 --> 05:34.090
I don't want her to get involved.

05:34.270 --> 05:36.760
But that doesn't mean you can
hide it from her.

05:36.760 --> 05:37.760
What else can I do?

05:39.360 --> 05:40.170
Tell her.

05:40.560 --> 05:42.120
And make her worry about me?

05:43.140 --> 05:44.730
You think you're protecting her.

05:44.730 --> 05:46.220
You think she can't do anything.

05:46.220 --> 05:47.550
Have you ever asked her?

05:47.800 --> 05:49.400
Anyway, everything I did was

05:50.240 --> 05:51.290
for her own good.

05:57.530 --> 05:58.460
For her own good?

06:01.850 --> 06:03.410
Do you know what she thinks?

06:03.440 --> 06:05.570
Why do you think it was for her own good?

06:06.650 --> 06:07.650
You think you know it better than me?

06:07.650 --> 06:08.850
I just know it better!

06:08.880 --> 06:10.050
You know what? I've heard the phrase,

06:10.050 --> 06:11.700
"for his good," too many times
since I was little.

06:11.700 --> 06:13.700
It's completely useless, you know?

06:16.680 --> 06:18.200
I don't want to argue with you.

06:18.200 --> 06:19.120
Brandy!

06:22.240 --> 06:23.970
Can you stop being so arrogant?

06:24.130 --> 06:26.390
There's no way you can keep this a secret.

06:27.120 --> 06:28.980
Today, she found out by accident.

06:29.300 --> 06:30.290
But what about next time?

06:30.290 --> 06:31.620
And the time after that?

06:31.880 --> 06:33.530
Are you going to hide it
every single time?

06:33.530 --> 06:34.409
Instead of letting others tell her,

06:34.409 --> 06:36.120
why don't you tell her yourself?

06:36.120 --> 06:37.780
Because I know what I'm doing!

06:38.690 --> 06:39.890
She's my girlfriend.

06:40.440 --> 06:41.970
I don't need you to teach me.

06:45.760 --> 06:46.440
Yes.

06:47.890 --> 06:49.220
She is your girlfriend.

06:53.850 --> 06:55.280
But she is Jiang Mu first!

07:22.120 --> 07:23.240
Why are you here?

07:23.970 --> 07:25.880
I'm here
because I want you to persuade Jin Zhao

07:25.880 --> 07:28.170
to stay away
from the Association's affairs.

07:28.170 --> 07:29.230
What Association?

07:30.050 --> 07:31.220
You don't need to know about that.

07:31.220 --> 07:32.570
Anyway, just talk to him.

07:32.570 --> 07:34.210
He'll listen to you.

07:34.800 --> 07:36.050
He's different from others.

07:36.050 --> 07:37.440
If he just works steadily,

07:37.440 --> 07:39.120
he'll make his mark someday.

07:39.360 --> 07:41.760
He shouldn't get involved in those things.

07:44.530 --> 07:45.530
What things?

07:47.170 --> 07:48.650
You wouldn't understand
even if I told you.

07:48.650 --> 07:50.380
I also overheard it from my dad.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.300
Anyway, just make sure he stays away
from the Association no matter what.

07:53.300 --> 07:54.960
The people there are dangerous.

07:54.960 --> 07:56.090
They'll eat him alive

07:56.090 --> 07:57.550
and leave nothing behind.

08:00.200 --> 08:00.880
Jiang Mu,

08:01.020 --> 08:03.000
you must try everything to persuade him

08:03.000 --> 08:04.930
to stay away from the Association.

08:04.970 --> 08:06.240
Tell him to quit

08:06.360 --> 08:08.090
whatever he's doing right now.

08:37.659 --> 08:38.380
Jin Zhao,

08:38.789 --> 08:39.980
I need to talk to you.

08:56.810 --> 08:57.600
Last night, I wasn't...

08:57.600 --> 08:58.410
I know.

09:01.200 --> 09:01.960
Zhao.

09:04.790 --> 09:06.600
No matter what you're planning to do,

09:06.600 --> 09:08.400
you must make sure you stay safe.

09:09.530 --> 09:11.010
Can you promise me that?

09:26.890 --> 09:27.650
I'll try.

09:41.720 --> 09:42.480
Are you

09:43.970 --> 09:45.630
doing those dangerous things

09:46.290 --> 09:47.890
for money?

09:49.790 --> 09:51.520
How did you find out about this?

09:54.120 --> 09:54.980
Was it Wan Qing?

09:59.410 --> 10:01.270
Did she ask you to talk me out of it?

10:07.110 --> 10:08.590
So you're quite loyal.

10:10.210 --> 10:11.010
Mom said

10:11.770 --> 10:13.230
that she'll sell the house

10:13.440 --> 10:14.770
and leave me some money.

10:15.800 --> 10:16.600
So

10:16.900 --> 10:18.100
would that be enough?

10:23.080 --> 10:24.010
Listen.

10:25.680 --> 10:27.080
It's not about the money.

10:28.680 --> 10:30.090
It's so late. You came all this way

10:30.090 --> 10:31.220
to ask me about this.

10:31.650 --> 10:32.650
Aren't you tired?

10:33.920 --> 10:35.850
Are you tired? I'll sleep with you.

10:39.680 --> 10:40.280
No, no, no.

10:40.560 --> 10:41.600
I mean,

10:41.850 --> 10:43.910
you sleep, and I'll stay by your side.

10:48.230 --> 10:49.040
Stay with me?

10:55.220 --> 10:57.080
Then hang on. Let me take a shower.

11:32.840 --> 11:34.170
What are you looking at?

11:34.560 --> 11:35.960
I'm looking at your book.

11:36.720 --> 11:38.120
Are you interested in it?

11:38.650 --> 11:39.560
Not really.

11:57.310 --> 11:58.350
In that Scramble

11:59.320 --> 12:01.410
I accidentally got involved in,

12:02.490 --> 12:05.130
was that bag the final prize?

12:07.900 --> 12:08.570
Yes.

12:10.370 --> 12:13.010
Who usually offers these prizes?

12:15.530 --> 12:16.730
Whoever organizes it

12:17.000 --> 12:18.130
provides the prize.

12:19.130 --> 12:20.370
Organize?

12:21.530 --> 12:22.840
Are you saying

12:23.130 --> 12:26.050
that there's a huge organization

12:26.390 --> 12:27.650
like the Association?

12:43.010 --> 12:45.260
Is that usually how the games are played?

12:45.260 --> 12:46.860
These casual games are rare.

12:47.930 --> 12:49.060
They're held occasionally.

12:49.060 --> 12:51.320
Only rich kids play these kinds of games.

12:53.210 --> 12:55.820
What about the serious games then?

12:59.320 --> 13:00.410
You've got some nerve asking that.

13:00.410 --> 13:02.270
You don't have the guts to answer?

13:07.210 --> 13:08.740
They are not anything good.

13:10.240 --> 13:11.900
The less you know, the better.

13:17.490 --> 13:19.600
Wan Qing was even willing
to humble herself,

13:19.600 --> 13:21.680
asking me to persuade Jin Zhao
to give up

13:21.680 --> 13:24.340
and not mess
with the Association's interests.

13:24.410 --> 13:25.560
What exactly is

13:26.180 --> 13:27.840
this so-called Association?

13:28.890 --> 13:31.890
Is it some sort
of dangerous underground organization?

13:31.890 --> 13:33.490
What on earth did Jin Zhao do?

13:53.360 --> 13:54.960
I'm just there to make money.

13:56.450 --> 13:57.920
Once I've earned enough, I'll leave.

13:57.920 --> 13:59.780
It's not like I'm killing anyone.

14:00.130 --> 14:01.330
What's the panic for?

14:04.720 --> 14:05.440
Then...

14:06.370 --> 14:09.100
Then how much longer are you
going to keep this up?

14:09.910 --> 14:10.620
Not long.

14:12.250 --> 14:13.310
It'll be over soon.

14:15.610 --> 14:16.800
How soon is "soon"?

14:18.510 --> 14:19.390
At most...

14:24.050 --> 14:24.720
Two weeks.

14:25.370 --> 14:26.200
Two weeks?

14:27.890 --> 14:28.890
So after 2 weeks,

14:29.600 --> 14:32.060
you won't do
such dangerous things anymore?

14:37.420 --> 14:38.110
Yes.

14:41.690 --> 14:42.650
I promise you.

15:30.160 --> 15:31.490
Did you catch anything?

15:38.770 --> 15:39.500
Here you are.

15:40.140 --> 15:40.870
Take a break.

16:06.890 --> 16:08.690
Looks like something's biting.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.770
That's my float.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.430
I know what to do.

16:13.910 --> 16:15.440
I don't need you to teach me.

16:18.370 --> 16:19.010
Fine.

16:25.400 --> 16:27.400
The float really seems to be moving.

16:29.360 --> 16:30.820
It's really moving! Look!

16:32.710 --> 16:34.110
Get the net! Quickly!

16:35.670 --> 16:36.870
Pull it over! Come on!

16:37.750 --> 16:38.650
Don't lose it!

16:38.680 --> 16:39.370
-Be careful.
-Pull it closer.

16:39.370 --> 16:40.480
-Catch it!
-Got it!

16:40.670 --> 16:41.470
Here it comes!

16:48.080 --> 16:50.280
You asked me to lift the rod, didn't you?

16:50.520 --> 16:52.580
And you asked me to get the net, right?

16:53.410 --> 16:54.780
Remove it now.

16:57.720 --> 16:58.980
You fished all day
and only caught this one?

16:58.980 --> 16:59.740
Be quiet.

17:09.960 --> 17:11.160
I've thought it over.

17:13.890 --> 17:14.750
You were right.

17:16.770 --> 17:17.920
I was too arrogant.

17:20.369 --> 17:21.970
I'm planning to find a chance

17:22.050 --> 17:24.180
to explain everything clearly to her.

17:48.380 --> 17:49.110
Brandy.

17:51.520 --> 17:53.390
You know my family's situation.

17:53.960 --> 17:55.240
My dad,

17:55.610 --> 17:56.940
for the sake of his pride

17:57.890 --> 17:59.690
and his so-called masculinity,

17:59.780 --> 18:01.040
never tells anyone in the family

18:01.040 --> 18:02.900
about anything that's happened.

18:03.240 --> 18:04.840
He says it's for our own good.

18:05.790 --> 18:07.140
But growing up,

18:07.800 --> 18:08.610
I've seen my mom

18:08.610 --> 18:11.010
get worried sick
and scared too many times.

18:13.260 --> 18:15.390
Do you really think that's good for us?

18:29.610 --> 18:30.570
You're my bro.

18:33.140 --> 18:34.340
Jiang Mu is my friend.

18:41.840 --> 18:44.040
I don't want you to follow my dad's path.

18:52.370 --> 18:53.240
I got it.

18:58.130 --> 19:00.130
The float's really moving!
Why didn't you tell me? Hey!

19:00.130 --> 19:01.190
Get the net! Hurry!

19:01.410 --> 19:02.680
Probably just trash again.

19:02.680 --> 19:03.440
Hurry!

19:04.760 --> 19:05.610
Pull it over.

19:08.000 --> 19:08.610
It's gone.

19:10.200 --> 19:10.890
It got away.

19:11.960 --> 19:12.920
So that was really a fish this time.

19:12.920 --> 19:15.050
It's all your fault that I lost my fish.

19:15.720 --> 19:16.610
Have a drink.

19:17.070 --> 19:19.600
-Drink and then take it easy to fish.
-The rod.

19:19.830 --> 19:21.490
You fish, and I'll net for you.

19:21.930 --> 19:24.480
It's because you came
and scared all the fish away.

19:24.480 --> 19:25.910
Did you catch a single one before I came?

19:25.910 --> 19:27.670
Of course I did! You're joking.

19:32.000 --> 19:35.390
[Speeding Auto House]

20:14.240 --> 20:14.930
Jiang Mu!

20:15.480 --> 20:16.540
Did you talk to him?

20:17.680 --> 20:18.680
Yes, I did.

20:19.410 --> 20:20.330
Did he agree?

20:20.720 --> 20:21.440
Yes.

20:22.740 --> 20:24.460
He said 2 weeks.

20:25.040 --> 20:25.850
After 2 weeks,

20:26.200 --> 20:28.370
he will stay away
from these dangerous things.

20:28.370 --> 20:29.170
I believe him.

20:29.200 --> 20:30.670
What's the use of your belief?

20:30.670 --> 20:31.370
You know what?

20:31.370 --> 20:33.630
He'll be in trouble before 2 weeks are up.

20:34.000 --> 20:34.760
Brandy!

20:36.090 --> 20:37.690
Brandy, we've got a problem!

20:39.440 --> 20:40.240
What's wrong?

20:40.250 --> 20:41.380
The car was smashed.

21:08.480 --> 21:09.540
Where's Iron Cock?

21:09.850 --> 21:11.210
He said his father was gravely ill

21:11.210 --> 21:13.610
and left
after a quick update this morning.

21:14.720 --> 21:16.420
I took an outside order this morning.
Then I saw

21:16.420 --> 21:17.520
the shop wasn't busy, so I went there.

21:17.520 --> 21:19.530
But when I arrived, I didn't see anyone.

21:19.530 --> 21:20.900
Master, I'm sorry.

21:20.930 --> 21:22.930
It was my fault for being negligent.

21:24.280 --> 21:26.100
It must be that old bastard
from Wan's who did it.

21:26.100 --> 21:27.100
So despicable.

21:27.480 --> 21:29.280
Sanlai, stop talking nonsense.

21:29.440 --> 21:30.840
Which eye of yours saw it?

21:39.530 --> 21:41.200
I-I really don't know anything about this.

21:41.200 --> 21:41.920
Get lost.

21:45.580 --> 21:46.340
Jin Zhao.

21:46.960 --> 21:48.050
Let me explain.

21:48.760 --> 21:50.170
I came here today to warn you.

21:50.170 --> 21:51.570
I would never mean to harm you.

21:51.570 --> 21:52.570
I said, get lost!

21:56.020 --> 21:58.150
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

22:11.250 --> 22:12.250
Fine, Jin Zhao.

22:14.100 --> 22:14.940
Listen.

22:15.560 --> 22:16.950
Whether you live or die,

22:18.160 --> 22:19.360
I won't care anymore.

22:37.330 --> 22:38.020
Sanlai,

22:39.000 --> 22:39.930
escort Mu home.

22:41.680 --> 22:42.400
Okay.

22:49.430 --> 22:50.150
Let's go.

22:55.900 --> 22:56.900
Check the things.

22:57.660 --> 22:58.550
Okay, Master.

23:19.870 --> 23:21.930
Do you remember when you were little,

23:22.750 --> 23:23.880
you failed your exam

23:24.170 --> 23:26.630
and were too scared
to ask your mom to sign it?

23:27.650 --> 23:29.050
After I signed it for you,

23:29.320 --> 23:32.320
the teacher found out
and called for a parent meeting.

23:32.720 --> 23:34.090
You cried your eyes out

23:34.870 --> 23:36.600
like it was the end of the world.

23:36.650 --> 23:37.650
I told you,

23:38.410 --> 23:39.540
"It's not a big deal.

23:40.370 --> 23:41.300
I can handle it."

23:41.850 --> 23:42.730
Remember that?

23:48.200 --> 23:49.130
Do you trust me?

23:51.630 --> 23:52.390
Yes, I do.

23:54.160 --> 23:56.020
Then go back to Jin Qiang's place,

23:56.160 --> 23:57.050
sleep well,

23:57.350 --> 23:58.410
and rest properly.

23:58.760 --> 24:00.090
Don't think about this mess.

24:00.090 --> 24:00.960
Cheer up,

24:01.650 --> 24:02.330
okay?

24:46.830 --> 24:47.420
He Zhang!

25:09.440 --> 25:10.040
Madam.

25:10.570 --> 25:11.330
Coming.

25:12.240 --> 25:12.810
Here.

25:13.990 --> 25:15.390
How about 2 more of these?

25:15.440 --> 25:16.090
Okay.

25:16.650 --> 25:17.250
All right.

25:17.510 --> 25:18.070
This one.

25:20.950 --> 25:21.810
Are these okay?

25:39.240 --> 25:40.090
T-That guy.

25:40.230 --> 25:42.760
That guy has been to the garage before,
right?

25:48.440 --> 25:49.370
I don't know him.

25:49.370 --> 25:50.240
You don't?

25:51.210 --> 25:53.890
I think I've seen him
at the garage before.

25:54.760 --> 25:55.890
Don't you remember?

25:57.480 --> 25:59.170
Do you know how many people come

25:59.170 --> 26:01.000
to the garage for car repair every day?

26:01.000 --> 26:02.200
I'm swamped.

26:02.520 --> 26:04.520
How can I remember everyone's face?

26:05.170 --> 26:06.280
But later, when we ran

26:06.280 --> 26:07.810
into this man at the market,

26:08.230 --> 26:10.270
Jin Zhao said
he had no impression of him at all.

26:10.270 --> 26:11.490
These will do.

26:11.520 --> 26:11.850
Yeah.

26:11.850 --> 26:12.850
See you next time.

26:12.890 --> 26:13.570
Bye-bye.

27:40.310 --> 27:41.110
Young lady.

27:49.130 --> 27:50.390
Are you looking for me?

27:50.570 --> 27:51.240
No, I'm not.

27:51.480 --> 27:54.680
If you're not looking for me,
why do you keep following me?

27:54.930 --> 27:57.410
I... I...

28:01.170 --> 28:02.350
I'm looking for my classmate.

28:02.350 --> 28:03.240
Pan Kai!

28:06.790 --> 28:07.850
Pan Kai, over here!

28:08.350 --> 28:09.440
Mu, what brings you here?

28:09.440 --> 28:10.760
What a coincidence!
Do you live around here?

28:10.760 --> 28:12.330
Yes, my dad's factory is just over there.

28:12.330 --> 28:13.990
I'm buying some fruit for him.

28:14.410 --> 28:15.140
That's nice.

28:18.000 --> 28:19.330
What are you doing here?

28:19.520 --> 28:20.650
I'm here to find someone.

28:20.650 --> 28:21.450
Find someone?

28:21.460 --> 28:22.270
Do I know them?

28:23.000 --> 28:24.660
I don't even know them myself.

28:25.760 --> 28:27.040
What fruit are you buying?

28:27.040 --> 28:28.060
I bought a mango.

28:28.090 --> 28:28.850
Pick some for me, too.

28:28.850 --> 28:29.960
-I also like mango.
-Okay!

28:29.960 --> 28:31.160
I'll buy some for you.

28:36.510 --> 28:37.980
Is this enough?

28:43.930 --> 28:46.130
That girl has been tailing me.

28:47.060 --> 28:49.020
She must know something.

28:50.810 --> 28:52.070
Handle it by yourself.

28:54.990 --> 28:55.600
Remember,

28:55.960 --> 28:58.760
your biggest rival in the mountain race is

28:59.200 --> 29:00.410
He Zhang from Wan's.

29:03.780 --> 29:04.510
Here you are.

29:07.130 --> 29:08.330
You need to defeat him

29:08.720 --> 29:09.890
and stay safe, too.

29:14.480 --> 29:15.050
Okay.

30:06.650 --> 30:07.650
Just as I thought.

30:08.810 --> 30:10.140
What do you mean by that?

30:15.090 --> 30:16.090
That person

30:16.750 --> 30:18.110
told you he saw me?

30:20.430 --> 30:21.630
You know way too much.

30:23.650 --> 30:26.380
You're not going to kill me
to silence me, are you?

30:28.310 --> 30:29.570
What do you think we do?

30:42.000 --> 30:44.800
Since you've already heard about me
from Wan Qing,

30:44.870 --> 30:46.530
you should know my situation.

30:47.370 --> 30:48.610
When I had worked for Wan Shengbang

30:48.610 --> 30:50.140
for about 2 and a half years,

30:50.850 --> 30:51.650
they occasionally

30:51.650 --> 30:53.780
had me do some jobs outside the garage.

31:07.480 --> 31:09.960
There was one time
when his driver had an accident.

31:09.960 --> 31:12.360
The deposit was paid,
but no one would race.

31:13.480 --> 31:14.480
So he turned to me.

31:15.200 --> 31:16.930
He wanted me to leave the garage

31:17.240 --> 31:18.500
and do this job for him.

31:20.520 --> 31:21.360
But I refused.

31:26.570 --> 31:28.830
Later, Jin Xin needed money for surgery.

31:29.240 --> 31:30.440
I wanted to help them,

31:31.050 --> 31:32.850
so I borrowed money from Sanlai.

31:33.410 --> 31:34.410
I bought a car,

31:36.040 --> 31:37.370
modified it overnight,

31:37.760 --> 31:39.220
and sold it at a high price.

31:42.810 --> 31:44.610
Later, that car had an accident.

31:45.200 --> 31:46.170
I always thought it was because

31:46.170 --> 31:47.700
of my technical oversight.

31:48.110 --> 31:50.110
I felt very guilty for those 2 years.

31:50.630 --> 31:52.560
I worked desperately to earn money

31:53.170 --> 31:54.700
to compensate that family.

31:57.340 --> 31:58.170
But later,

31:59.290 --> 32:00.950
I realized it wasn't my fault.

32:03.850 --> 32:06.040
Wan Dayong tampered with that car.

32:07.330 --> 32:08.480
I was set up.

32:10.890 --> 32:12.410
After that, I left Wan's.

32:13.890 --> 32:16.020
That's when Officer Lu approached me.

32:17.160 --> 32:19.700
Officer Lu is
from the Anti-smuggling Bureau.

32:19.700 --> 32:21.560
They were working on a major case.

32:22.590 --> 32:25.120
At first,
they just wanted some leads from me.

32:25.440 --> 32:27.440
Until later, when I approached him.

32:28.480 --> 32:30.080
That was after your arrival.

32:30.720 --> 32:32.240
What they're investigating isn't

32:32.240 --> 32:33.440
Wan Shengbang at all,

32:35.280 --> 32:37.440
nor is it any street racing organization.

32:37.440 --> 32:39.240
Through illegal street racing,

32:39.900 --> 32:41.500
they're trying to track down

32:42.250 --> 32:43.910
the smuggling gang behind it.

32:46.520 --> 32:48.720
But this Association is very cautious.

32:49.280 --> 32:51.370
Having someone infiltrate it
out of nowhere is

32:51.370 --> 32:52.500
simply impossible.

32:53.070 --> 32:55.890
Your points in the Association
must reach the top ranks

32:55.890 --> 32:58.290
for you to get noticed
by those higher-ups.

32:59.880 --> 33:01.080
Brandy!

33:01.570 --> 33:03.280
I've told you

33:03.530 --> 33:05.640
that we don't allow outsiders here.

33:08.200 --> 33:10.770
Anti-smuggling Bureau officers
found it hard to infiltrate

33:10.770 --> 33:11.850
until I came along.

33:13.280 --> 33:14.330
I told Officer Lu

33:15.240 --> 33:17.370
that I could keep racing and competing

33:17.720 --> 33:18.810
to earn points

33:19.000 --> 33:20.400
and get into the alliance

33:21.000 --> 33:23.000
to gather the information he needs.

33:25.140 --> 33:27.000
I'm ranked in the top 10 in points.

33:32.440 --> 33:34.170
If someone had to do this job,

33:36.440 --> 33:37.720
I'd be the best choice.

33:40.400 --> 33:42.800
Because you had racing experience before,

33:42.930 --> 33:45.590
those in the Association
wouldn't suspect you.

33:46.520 --> 33:47.250
Quite smart.

33:52.680 --> 33:53.370
However,

33:54.680 --> 33:56.480
that was only part of the reason.

33:59.230 --> 34:01.890
I had an opportunity
that was beyond suspicion.

34:02.530 --> 34:04.530
They thought I was getting involved

34:05.130 --> 34:07.330
due to my grudge against Wan Shengbang.

34:09.159 --> 34:10.489
I had fallen out with him

34:10.690 --> 34:11.440
and gone against him.

34:11.440 --> 34:12.290
I heard

34:12.750 --> 34:15.690
that you're planning to interfere
with the business in Xikouguan.

34:15.690 --> 34:17.350
Quite ambitious, aren't you?

34:17.550 --> 34:19.650
Whether I interfere
or not isn't up to you.

34:19.650 --> 34:20.980
It's not up to me either.

34:21.120 --> 34:22.409
We'll see who has what it takes.

34:22.409 --> 34:23.639
You're really something,

34:23.639 --> 34:24.929
climbing the ranks ahead of others

34:24.929 --> 34:25.770
and getting so much attention

34:25.770 --> 34:27.330
in such a short time.

34:27.690 --> 34:28.860
Aren't you obviously

34:28.860 --> 34:30.610
going against Mr. Wan?

34:30.810 --> 34:31.730
Listen!

34:32.080 --> 34:33.040
Don't be naive.

34:33.210 --> 34:35.010
It's not too late to back off now.

34:35.520 --> 34:37.560
Although this is just one factor.

34:39.830 --> 34:41.230
What about the others?

34:42.440 --> 34:43.900
Officer Lu promised me...

34:46.460 --> 34:48.150
As long as we solve this case,

34:50.440 --> 34:52.170
he will make sure Wan Shengbang

34:52.560 --> 34:54.590
and his accomplices are
brought to justice.

34:54.590 --> 34:56.120
Once they're under arrest,

34:59.810 --> 35:01.670
I can successfully clear my name.

35:08.040 --> 35:09.970
The street racing organization is

35:10.000 --> 35:11.290
actually just a front.

35:12.960 --> 35:14.560
They use street racing

35:15.380 --> 35:16.150
to observe

35:16.290 --> 35:19.090
and groom people
who can take over their business.

35:21.350 --> 35:23.000
Not everyone has the capability

35:23.000 --> 35:25.480
and mental fortitude to handle this job.

35:26.290 --> 35:27.770
Only those top scorers in the alliance

35:27.770 --> 35:28.700
can get noticed.

35:29.080 --> 35:30.540
It's because these people

35:30.960 --> 35:32.620
all share some common traits.

35:33.730 --> 35:34.600
They're brave,

35:35.930 --> 35:36.770
reckless,

35:38.040 --> 35:38.900
and need money.

35:42.300 --> 35:43.140
600 HP!

35:44.040 --> 35:45.080
650 HP!

35:46.260 --> 35:48.380
It looks like RX7 has gone past 700 HP.

35:48.770 --> 35:50.120
Brandy, you're going hard tonight.

35:50.120 --> 35:53.050
You've already qualified.
No need to risk your life.

35:54.930 --> 35:56.560
So they damaged your car

35:57.000 --> 35:59.530
because they didn't want you
to join the race?

36:04.290 --> 36:05.420
Wan Shengbang knows

36:06.080 --> 36:08.480
that if our dispute
comes out into the open,

36:08.690 --> 36:11.090
the alliance won't stand by
and do nothing.

36:11.690 --> 36:13.150
There's only one solution

36:13.600 --> 36:15.120
that can settle this matter.

36:15.120 --> 36:16.370
What solution?

36:19.930 --> 36:21.130
According to custom,

36:22.000 --> 36:24.460
if both parties can't reconcile privately,

36:24.890 --> 36:27.600
they shall resort
to the most traditional solution,

36:27.600 --> 36:29.130
settling it with a car race.

36:30.770 --> 36:31.810
The losing side

36:32.850 --> 36:35.380
must not cause trouble
for the other anymore.

36:35.560 --> 36:36.490
This is the rule.

36:40.750 --> 36:42.370
Can your car be fixed then?

36:46.040 --> 36:46.900
It can be fixed.

36:48.110 --> 36:49.470
But I need some parts.

36:52.410 --> 36:53.470
More importantly,

36:55.520 --> 36:57.520
I need to find a reliable repair shop

36:57.730 --> 36:59.260
willing to take on this job.

37:00.690 --> 37:01.950
I want to clear my name.

37:02.890 --> 37:04.420
Especially since you came,

37:05.850 --> 37:07.250
I've wanted it even more.

37:08.690 --> 37:10.000
I want to prove myself,

37:12.120 --> 37:13.380
to prove that at least,

37:13.800 --> 37:15.130
I'm still worthy of you.

37:19.410 --> 37:20.810
Actually, on my way here,

37:25.940 --> 37:28.210
I was thinking about
how to smooth over this issue

37:28.210 --> 37:29.540
to put your mind at ease.

37:33.040 --> 37:35.770
But when I was almost here,
I realized something.

37:38.440 --> 37:40.600
If I told a lie for now

37:40.930 --> 37:42.330
to cover up this problem,

37:42.850 --> 37:43.910
then in the future,

37:46.800 --> 37:48.640
I would have to come up
with all kinds of excuses

37:48.640 --> 37:49.770
to maintain that lie

37:49.820 --> 37:51.370
and keep you worrying.

37:53.260 --> 37:54.520
Instead of doing that,

37:55.150 --> 37:56.950
I might as well come clean to you.

38:06.940 --> 38:07.590
Mu,

38:10.290 --> 38:11.820
I've explained everything

38:12.080 --> 38:13.140
that I can explain.

38:15.770 --> 38:17.030
Go back to hit the sack,

38:17.830 --> 38:18.630
okay?

38:24.440 --> 38:26.560
This thing sounds super dangerous.

38:27.040 --> 38:28.500
Do you really have to do it?

38:42.330 --> 38:44.590
I can't let them keep doing evil anymore.

38:47.520 --> 38:48.520
This is something

38:49.250 --> 38:50.370
only I can handle.

38:54.580 --> 38:55.420
Even if

38:59.900 --> 39:01.540
it means sacrificing myself.
